These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different games are played: domino, canasta, whist, monopoly
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, fuchsia, black, green
City: liverpool, hannover, berlin, venice
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, begonia, daffodil, sunflower
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, helicopter, taxi, tram
 1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 2. the person traveling to venice is between the person playing domino and the person driving the tram##2
 3. the person who growsamaryllis is the person driving the tram##1
 4. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 5. the person driving the car is between the person playing domino and the person traveling to berlin##2
 6. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is the person playing whist##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who likes green##1
 9. the person who likes black is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
10. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Game           | whist | domino   | monopoly | canasta |
| Color   | amber      | fuchsia | black              | green |
| City   | liverpool       | hannover     | venice               | berlin    |
| Flower           | begonia        | daffodil     | sunflower           | amaryllis       |
| Transport     | helicopter | taxi     | car                | tram      |

