.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-2::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, lemon, pineapple, tomato
City: venice, liverpool, hamburg, paris
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, reading, board-games, card-games
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, tea, coffee
4 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, monopoly, canasta
 1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 3. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person eating pineapple and the person drinking fanta##2
 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person playing billiard##1
 5. the person drinking tea is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 7. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 8. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 9. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
10. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person playing billiard is the person eating pineapple##1
12. the person eating blueberry is the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Food          | pineapple       | lemon      | blueberry      | tomato      |
| City           | paris | liverpool | hamburg | venice |
| Hobby   | card-games          | reading       | board-games            | rock-climbing      |
| Beverage           | cola            | tea    | fanta           | coffee       |
| Game         | billiard        | backgammon    | monopoly         | canasta  |

