4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, swisher, chaman, baccarat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, rugby, skiing, water-polo
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
 2. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
 3. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 4. the cain-smoker is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 5. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is between the person who likes ebony and the person who's sport is golf##2
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 8. the person watching western movies is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is the baccarat-smoker##1
10. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
