.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, pink, apricot, amber
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, october, september, november
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, house, jazz, pop
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, lily, marigold, aconite
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, rat, goat, snake
 1. the owner of the goat is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 2. the owner of the rat is between the fan of disco and the fan of house##2
 3. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
 4. the person who likes apricot is the person who growsbellflower##1
 5. the fan of house is between the person who growsbellflower and the owner of the rabbit##2
 6. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1
 7. the person who growslily is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 8. the person who likes brown is the owner of the snake##1
 9. the person who likes pink is between the owner of the rat and the fan of jazz##2
10. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Color      | amber     | pink | apricot    | brown          |
| Birthday          | november | may     | september | october         |
| Music-Genre   | jazz    | house       | pop         | disco        |
| Flower         | aconite  | lily     | bellflower     | marigold |
| Pet     | rabbit     | goat      | rat   | snake          |

