 3. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
 6. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 7. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the pilot##1
 8. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
10. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in december and the doctor##2
11. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
12. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
