House: victorian, cape-cod, craftsman, wooden
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, azalea, balloon-flower, amaryllis
 1. the musician is on the right of the dancer##1
 2. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 3. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 5. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 6. the wooden house is the dressmaker##1
 7. the victorian house is the dancer##1
 8. the musician is between the dressmaker and the person driving the ship##2
 9. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the fish is between the person driving the ship and the owner of the hedgehog##2
11. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Transport          | ship       | subway       | helicopter | bus    |
