There 4 different types of food: banana, carrot, peas, potato
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, amber, brown, apricot
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, police-officer, scientist, chef
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, traveling, sudoku, puzzles
 1. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the chef##1
 3. the scientist is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person playing domino##2
 4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
 5. the dancer is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 6. the person eating banana is on the far right##1
 7. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 8. the person who likes apricot is the person eating carrot##1
 9. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
10. the person eating potato is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
11. the dancer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |    4     |
| Game      | domino | canasta       | scrabble  | chess |
| Food          | peas     | potato     | carrot | banana   |
| Color   | amber      | brown | apricot | emerald  |
| Job           | police-officer     | scientist       | chef  | dancer      |
| Hobby     | gardening | puzzles      | sudoku | traveling      |

