 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is the doctor##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is the social-worker##1
 6. the person watching romance movies is the japanese##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is the nigerian##1
 8. the japanese is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 9. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in fishinging##1
11. the person who's birthday is in fishinging is between the social-worker and the person who's hobby is chess##2
12. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the japanese##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality      | indian      | japanese         | nigerian | thai      |
| Job           | social-worker | police-officer | designer | doctor     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure         | romance          | comedy  | action |
| Birthday         | july        | fishinging  | june | may   |
| Hobby     | fishing    | sudoku         | chess     | card-games     |

