 5. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking juice and the person who's birthday is in september##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
 7. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far right##1
 8. the bolivar-smoker is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1

