.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, horror, western, romance
House: ranch-style, tower, modern, townhouse
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, malaysian, pakistani, thai
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, lilac, mauve, ivory
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, april, july, march
 1. the townhouse house is the malaysian##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in march is between the thai and the person who likes light-blue##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who likes lilac and the person who's birthday is in july##2
 4. the tower house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 5. the modern house is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 6. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 8. the modern house is the person who likes mauve##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
10. the person watching action movies is the japanese##1
11. the japanese is the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Movie-Genre         | western  | horror | romance | action |
| House   | townhouse      | tower   | modern      | ranch-style    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | pakistani | thai        | japanese     |
| Color         | light-blue  | lilac  | mauve     | ivory      |
| Birthday     | november | march      | april   | july       |

 